description:
For an international project in Chennai, we are urgently looking for a Full Remote Mobile App Developer.










 We are looking for a motivated contractor. Candidates need to be fluent in English.










**Tasks and responsibilities:** 



* Development of IOS and Android mobile app using ionic framework;
* Building and deploying app both in Apple app store and Google Play store;
* Connecting to various data sources, importing data and binding to mobile dashboard;
* Implementing mobile native features;
* Work with custom Capacitor plugins and create custom plugins when required;
* Developing app with rich visualization and enable user friendly interface using market leading tools;









**Profile:** 



* Bachelor or Master degree;
* 5\\+ years of years of hands\\-on IOS mobile app development expertise in ionic framework with market leading tools;
* Experience in various development methodology like Agile/Scrum development methodology;
* Experience in Data/Web Services Technology;
* Experience in developing IOS and Android mobile app in ionic framework;
* Experience in implementing mobile native features;
* Experience with custom Capacitor plugins;
* Fluent in English;
